**IMPORTANCE OF MITOSIS:**

**1. Growth:**
 Baby  child  adult (trillions of cell divisions)
 Plant seedling  mature tree

**2. Repair and Regeneration:**
 Wound healing (skin cells divide to close cut)
 Bone healing after fracture
