NIGHT (Land Breeze):
🌙 Land cools faster than sea
🌡️ Warm air rises over sea
💨 Cool air from land moves to sea
= Breeze from land to sea
\`\`\`

**Convection in Everyday Life:**
• Air conditioning - cool air sinks, warm air rises, creating circulation
